Package: CGMprocessing
Title: Clean CGM analysis in Diabetes clinical research
Version: 5.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alice", "Carr", , "acarr1@ualberta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0704-8843"))
Description: Package containing functions cleaning and analysing CGM data
    for clinical studies. Definitions for CGM output metrics are inline
    with International Consensus for CGM Analysis (Danne 2017). Also
    includes specific function to aid CGM analysis in the context of
    exercise studies, with specific outputs inline with exercise
    recommendations (Riddell 2017).
